            "segment": {
              "startIndex": 473,
              "endIndex": 1066,
              "text": "### Quick Comparison\n| Factor | Microneedling | Chemical Peel |\n| :--- | :--- | :--- |\n| **Best For** | Deep texture, rolling, and boxcar scars | Pigmentation (dark spots), surface texture |\n| **How it Works** | Micro-needles trigger collagen production | Acids dissolve top skin layers to reveal new skin |\n| **Skin Tone** | Safe for all skin tones (low PIH risk) | Higher risk of discoloration for darker skin |\n| **Downtime** | 1–3 days (redness, like a sunburn) | 1–10 days (depending on peel depth/strength) |\n| **Sessions** | Usually 3–6 sessions | Varies widely (1–6 sessions) |"
            },
            "groundingChunkIndices": [
