          {
            "segment": {
              "startIndex": 1619,
              "endIndex": 1747,
              "text": "*   **Ice Pick Scars (narrow, deep \"holes\"):** Neither standard microneedling nor standard peels are highly effective for these."
            },
            "groundingChunkIndices": [
              6
            ]
          },
          {
            "segment": {
              "startIndex": 2526,
              "endIndex": 2619,
              "text": "### The Case for Combination Therapy\nDermatologists often recommend a \"multi-modal\" approach."
